               <msContents class="#MTM">
                  <summary><p>A multiple-text manuscript containing three works, notably in praise of Gaṇeśa:
  <list rend="numbered">
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Piḷḷaiyār Akaval</title> 1, that is, <title xml:lang="ta">Vināyakar Akaval</title> attributed to Auvaiyār (Zvelebil 1995, p. 770) (U2).</item>
    <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Piḷḷaiyār Akaval</title> 2 (U3).</item>
    <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Iraṭṭai Maṇimālai</title>, that is, <title xml:lang="ta">Mayilaviraṭṭai Maṇimālai</title> (U4). In 21 stanzas: the <foreign xml:lang="ta">Kāppu</foreign> + 20 numbered stanzas.</item>
  </list>
</p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (February 2021 and June 2021).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p> 

    </summary>
                  
